MriWatcher 2.3 (Aug 21, 2013) -- nitrc svn revision 17

New Features:
- Redesign the GUI layout to work better for modern computer display
- Rewriten the view options' algorithm
- Add more key shortcut and give more user tips

Fixed Issues:
- Take back the orientation options, which cause the wrong pixel intensity show up


